# Trivy Ignore File for GCRF Library Management System
# Version: 1.0.0
# Last Updated: 2025-11-01
#
# This file contains CVEs that are intentionally ignored due to:
# - False positives
# - Accepted risks with compensating controls
# - Not applicable to our use case
#
# Format: CVE-YYYY-XXXXX [expiry date] [reason]
#
# IMPORTANT: Each ignored CVE must have:
# 1. Expiry date (YYYY-MM-DD) for periodic review
# 2. Clear justification
# 3. Approval from security team
#
# Review schedule: Monthly review of all ignored CVEs

#==============================================================================
# Example Ignored CVEs (Remove when adding real entries)
#==============================================================================

# CVE-2024-12345 exp:2025-12-31
# Reason: False positive - vulnerability in feature we don't use
# Justification: Affected function not exposed in our configuration
# Approved by: Security Team, 2025-11-01

# CVE-2024-67890 exp:2025-12-31
# Reason: Requires physical access to exploit, server is in secure datacenter
# Compensating controls: Physical access restricted, monitored 24/7
# Approved by: Security Team, 2025-11-01

